quote>凌晨一點</blockquote><br />\n食完搭的士?</blockquote><br />\n唔通行？<br />\n用腦<br />\n無錢搭唔好學人去"},{"pid":"2f4d468737f9503006d9f0672dc8ee9c8805e7b9","tid":351434,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>凌晨一點</blockquote><br />\n食完搭的士?</blockquote><br />\n食完食女店員啦on9"},{"pid":"646258ed6b24866c0d6d2d89e86ce37e56c2202a","tid":351434,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>凌晨一點</blockquote><br />\n食完搭的士?</blockquote><br />\n唔通行？<br />\n用腦<br />\n無錢搭唔好學人去</blockquote><br />\n住附近咪得囉，新宿大把酒店啦"},{"pid":"16675296233f286eb3c158f2c773214203894997","tid":351434,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:01:38.000Z","msg":"HI"},{"pid":"f8b18886d3cd0918570664dddbcb9fa84b4e2353","tid":351434,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好像好好食，但又唔想排，11月先去，住新宿<br />\n<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你住新宿應該非常近，搭乜鬼的士呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0346956b11d85c091d6bc8a03b789b64f72db4a7","tid":351434,"uid":16568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"間野越嚟越唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5274e218e78fef0b7b2d946613d6e324c71e14","tid":351434,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HI</blockquote><br />\n一睇就知你係香港個間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪扮日本個間啦"},{"pid":"fef6c8b7dd1c627e01cd02e2a3dde7d1fe08b69e","tid":351434,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間野越嚟越唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想知邊間野會出名之後越做越好，求推介加指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36df03b3e4d859dbd8f54d4ee7cee79e6bc3d35","tid":351434,"uid":19091,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"我都覺得越做越差 幾年前第一次食覺得好食  但上個月去完覺得退步左<br />\n<br />\n東京可以試下afuri<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60cac131d60d53aad5b6e0b14e6636a1c69e6fe","tid":351434,"uid":23696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:07:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺得越做越差 幾年前第一次食覺得好食  但上個月去完覺得退步左<br />\n<br />\n東京可以試下afuri<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵下先"},{"pid":"c39ae52bdc261066b8f2615412413a4cab35ebb9","tid":351434,"uid":23696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你想太多了吧！唔想排太耐就一係一開門即去，一係10點零11點去。其實如果你住新宿附近，咁就走幾轉啦，想食好野係要付出代價的！其實最多等半小時或者九個字到，合理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝兄弟"},{"pid":"6a8067a14fc4cd3b9c5e3cea9a23a7d5c1c7eaad","tid":351434,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺得越做越差 幾年前第一次食覺得好食  但上個月去完覺得退步左<br />\n<br />\n東京可以試下afuri<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本人就係咁，第一次食永遠是最好，之後隔一段時間再食，已經成件事唔同左，因為冇左新鮮感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43d9b81aa25e53350a9dbb131bee14a8c73451c","tid":351434,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>HI</blockquote><br />\n一睇就知你係香港個間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪扮日本個間啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14125e9d419f0f6a4b3688c5527eaf0c09e48a73","tid":351434,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你想太多了吧！唔想排太耐就一係一開門即去，一係10點零11點去。其實如果你住新宿附近，咁就走幾轉啦，想食好野係要付出代價的！其實最多等半小時或者九個字到，合理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝兄弟</blockquote><br />\n客氣啦，玩得開心D！記得食埋日本妹先好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6055d8f2247f4577ba4d25fac8b6e70a49ce9369","tid":351434,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"上次凌晨一點食 排左2個字就入得<br />\n(住附近)"},{"pid":"3d448fcedbe77e03dcab21a9d6799d218f69e787","tid":351434,"uid":23696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>HI</blockquote><br />\n一睇就知你係香港個間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪扮日本個間啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵到你啦"},{"pid":"3fb9852253ad4de3d1a91a4f89be72fbbd67de88","tid":351434,"uid":23696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你想太多了吧！唔想排太耐就一係一開門即去，一係10點零11點去。其實如果你住新宿附近，咁就走幾轉啦，想食好野係要付出代價的！其實最多等半小時或者九個字到，合理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝兄弟</blockquote><br />\n客氣啦，玩得開心D！記得食埋日本妹先好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為<em>池袋</em>無咩野行咁，去都係想食好野"},{"pid":"b2f805752b977a7fcfdc9c040b34b271a74a197a","tid":351434,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你想太多了吧！唔想排太耐就一係一開門即去，一係10點零11點去。其實如果你住新宿附近，咁就走幾轉啦，想食好野係要付出代價的！其實最多等半小時或者九個字到，合理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝兄弟</blockquote><br />\n客氣啦，玩得開心D！記得食埋日本妹先好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為<em>池袋</em>無咩野行咁，去都係想食好野</blockquote><br />\n池袋都好多野行"},{"pid":"85fc7460e63eb99afcd6f0b520d62eafb3a30f21","tid":351434,"uid":35178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺得越做越差 幾年前第一次食覺得好食  但上個月去完覺得退步左<br />\n<br />\n東京可以試下afuri<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢間係幾好食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平日去唔駛等直入。"},{"pid":"f11a32e876afae34795bfa10da0e850f85400b8b","tid":351434,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你想太多了吧！唔想排太耐就一係一開門即去，一係10點零11點去。其實如果你住新宿附近，咁就走幾轉啦，想食好野係要付出代價的！其實最多等半小時或者九個字到，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 合理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝兄弟</blockquote><br />\n客氣啦，玩得開心D！記得食埋日本妹先好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為<em>池袋</em>無咩野行咁，去都係想食好野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/131252_60fa23d44b5ce4b45f14c8fd65daccc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F131252_60fa23d44b5ce4b45f14c8fd65daccc6.jpg&h=cbd027b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得買呢個，好似東京車站有，超好食"},{"pid":"2195582e53249cb909b162e8eb85efb4df3da0d7","tid":351434,"uid":28879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>凌晨一點</blockquote><br />\n食完搭的士?</blockquote><br />\nGoogle map話行返新宿要一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想行就俾錢搭的士體驗下</blockquote><br />\n的士囉 舊拎水"},{"pid":"580684223e40d72e973219e186707875bb90c713","tid":351434,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>凌晨一點</blockquote><br />\n食完搭的士?</blockquote><br />\nGoogle map話行返新宿要一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想行就俾錢搭的士體驗下</blockquote><br />\n的士囉 舊拎水</blockquote><br />\n佢住新宿駛鬼搭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601d7c66e9350e95c9a4a6474c4d39c97eb14511","tid":351434,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:19:40.000Z","msg":"住新宿食乜鬼無敵家. 食凪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10ad8a7e87c13766d75569d7b28ea760df2b10b","tid":351434,"uid":23696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住新宿食乜鬼無敵家. 食凪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"