</blockquote><br />\n我早排去 4點去都等左半個鐘"},{"pid":"93721a85cf1060f58960f4122e5bf25f4971cfb6","tid":351434,"uid":23696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平日4-5點等左十分鐘就入到</blockquote><br />\n咁爽快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我早排去 4點去都等左半個鐘</blockquote><br />\n半個鐘都可以接受"},{"pid":"7a61e36ae1e06cb880ca7af0f8d48f80c399996b","tid":351434,"uid":111975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:20:11.000Z","msg":"上次閒日walk in 1點就有位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664bc36f470358a03d7296ae6cbb21cb1e7bad59","tid":351434,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"唔值得吹捧"},{"pid":"ed642400188ae60e02999a3581d7f8877a2752e4","tid":351434,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:23:46.000Z","msg":"住左係池袋幾年，都冇想過去食<br />\n差唔多日日經過都見成堆香港人排隊<br />\n我就真係唔會咁on9去排<br />\n又唔係得佢一間"},{"pid":"6f6d5de30d4c5497431b8b28eaac572c89e9d78d","tid":351434,"uid":23696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住左係池袋幾年，都冇想過去食<br />\n差唔多日日經過都見成堆香港人排隊<br />\n我就真係唔會咁on9去排<br />\n又唔係得佢一間</blockquote><br />\n其實係咪間間差不多"},{"pid":"6bd9ce01e7e8fc3ea3b82a7e8d8e9ea7cfb33a09","tid":351434,"uid":25025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"食咗次 無乜特別<br />\n仲要排成粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec69710e0ae6fcfac895b9f70080836642485a62","tid":351434,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:00:18.000Z","msg":"一星期前...先食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n任何一間都好食過佢啦, 垃圾<br />\n<br />\n行遠幾步 食一風堂都無咁嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176ea89653266e07dc7bcec8306eaee8058fd4af","tid":351434,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你想太多了吧！唔想排太耐就一係一開門即去，一係10點零11點去。其實如果你住新宿附近，咁就走幾轉啦，想食好野係要付出代價的！其實最多等半小時或者九個字到，合理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝兄弟</blockquote><br />\n客氣啦，玩得開心D！記得食埋日本妹先好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為<em>池袋</em>無咩野行咁，去都係想食好野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n池袋好多野行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dab625cd0d9f5e697f417f49640b435b15b81cd","tid":351434,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:02:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食咗次 無乜特別<br />\n仲要排成粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔抵排9個字 <br />\n<br />\n上星期食"},{"pid":"ec0e9a7148ae8b9f203dd651d227b7e1091abe07","tid":351434,"uid":31470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:04:39.000Z","msg":"其實無敵家幾難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有心搵嘅，押上Skytree附近有一間唔錯"},{"pid":"a8c36580ffaf8c968df44778806e57a713a421f0","tid":351434,"uid":116685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"個人覺得無敵家好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e78642c4bb5c22d2a5185233e2ebeb161b3ff83","tid":351434,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:07:57.000Z","msg":"有次冬天凍到仆街走去食<br />\n因為去左十幾廿次東京都未食過 就試下有幾把炮<br />\n等左半個鐘有多 凍撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得舊肉又太肥 碗野又無特別"},{"pid":"1d3d0c724738c78b81278940ccb18e35626e8174","tid":351434,"uid":15200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"屌果次夜晚10點半去池袋 等左成個鐘郁得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61581955e41bdd1d809d7afcedcad8c946033a69","tid":351434,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好像好好食，但又唔想排，11月先去，住新宿<br />\n<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你住新宿應該非常近，搭乜鬼的士呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新宿無敵家唔係同一個老闆<br />\n池袋行返新宿你行喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360a3948c127e906dd4cf64a7e2b298248f1ec4e","tid":351434,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/151628_cf8d81fe502973cb00bb544e9b02b688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F151628_cf8d81fe502973cb00bb544e9b02b688.jpg&h=ba02a69f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/151628_8dae6c189ccbd7e501c82d30aa99c4fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F151628_8dae6c189ccbd7e501c82d30aa99c4fb.jpg&h=100c69a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個湯其實幾好，但啲叉燒無乜特別。<br />\n想食好西梗係去築地，又唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015b04b0963639508e474d14e83d2100e5271e41","tid":351434,"uid":25025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/151628_cf8d81fe502973cb00bb544e9b02b688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F151628_cf8d81fe502973cb00bb544e9b02b688.jpg&h=ba02a69f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/151628_8dae6c189ccbd7e501c82d30aa99c4fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F151628_8dae6c189ccbd7e501c82d30aa99c4fb.jpg&h=100c69a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個湯其實幾好，但啲叉燒無乜特別。<br />\n想食好西梗係去築地，又唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n築地間間都勁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇邊間推介"},{"pid":"071484de76191db7f37fab1c4b3ab456796f3868","tid":351434,"uid":15237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T08:31:04.000Z","msg":"好難食 唔值"},{"pid":"ace428b5eab86978e4ec4f38c37fc0206a3247e4","tid":351434,"uid":23696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"感謝各位，睇來我都是放棄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a30d8afdb68feec891300396d57c59c2d8b5ad7","tid":351434,"uid":68444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:48:25.000Z","msg":"我試過下午4:30唔使排"},{"pid":"ea05b88e9ed2e9e23b2f8ea26a9d7d6a4fad3eb1","tid":351434,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:21:29.000Z","msg":"之前食飯時間去排一個鐘都唔洗<br />\n講耐麵屋一燈仲耐啦 開舖去排咗個半鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}